Abezimo eziphuthumayo kwa-ER24 nabezinye izinkampani zezimo eziphuthumayo bathole umbiko ngale ngozi kuyoshaya * -6 ntambama base benikela kule ndawo. Okhulumela abakwa-ER24, uMnuz Russel Meiring, uthe ngesikhathi befika lapho bebizelwe khona bathole iveni nemoto encane kumile emizileni ehlukene emgwaqweni. Abantu batholwe besaphazeke emgwaqweni. Uthe bahlole abalimele bathola ukuthi bangu-11. Abanye bebelimele okungatheni. Uthe ngenhlanhla akekho umuntu obelimele kakhulu noma oshonile. Abalimele banikwe usizo endaweni yesehlo base bephuthunyiswa ezibhedlela eziseduze ukuze balashwe. UMeiring uthe imbangela yengozi ayaziwa kodwa amaphoyisa abekhona endaweni yesehlo ukuze aphenye.   